{"tid":1068120,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想死","createTime":"2019-03-19T04:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T11:23:56.000Z","uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0eeaf01f9b1d7379a59ac93c488c0403a8bea4","tid":1068120,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aaa5d32c9ac97367b769e7f91b5537e15825b16","tid":1068120,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"飲酒"},{"pid":"d7b6a38efc1fc1ca4a350e00591f22a0baecc461","tid":1068120,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f0eeaf01f9b1d7379a59ac93c488c0403a8bea4","tid":1068120,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"看來你心中的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀．．．人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=54a6207e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=de16ce92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"be321655fa92f761a009d90b5c8050633b73be56","tid":1068120,"uid":155628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"巴打 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}